(1174, '<div class="shop-about clearfix">\r\n<div class="col-1">\r\n<div class="tab-container">\r\n	<div class="tab-title">\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li><a class="active" href="#" data-tab="tab-beauty">Balanced Aesthetics</a></li>\r\n			<li><a href="#" data-tab="tab-usda">Organic Certification</a></li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		<div class="clear"></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="tab-content">\r\n		<div class="active text tab-beauty">\r\n			<div class="logo"><img src="{{media url="wysiwyg/small-banner.png"}}" alt="" /></div>\r\n			<p>Let’s start experiencing beautiful glowing skin by balancing water and oil with Balanced Aesthetics by Renguangdo.</p>\r\n                        <p>Balanced Aesthetics is the harmonization of multi-facet wisdom incorporating nurturing of body, mind and soul. RenGuangDo combination of the traditional wisdom and modern technology, for developing quality grooming and skincare products based upon the unique platform of Pure Camellia Seed Oil.</p>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<div class="clear"></div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="text tab-usda">\r\n			<div class="logo"><img src="{{media url="wysiwyg/small-banner-2.png"}}" alt="" /></div>\r\n			<p>USDA organic certification is approved by the U.S. Department of Agriculture authorized official organic certification mark, to prove that the raw materials are in compliance with strict rules of production processes, and to prohibit the use of pesticides, chemical fertilizers, growth hormones, chemical pesticides, herbicides, synthetic substitutes, GM material and eliminate risk factors radiation. Also, the product must contain at least 95% or more organic ingredients, in order to use the round USDA organic label mark on the product, which is complete and reliable international organic mark.</p>\r\n			<p>RenGuangDo use Pure Camellia Seed Oil (USDA Certified) as a creative platform for the production of a series of high-quality skin and hair care products to cater for the various needs of a variety of skin and hair.</p>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<div class="clear"></div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<script type="text/javascript">\r\n(function($) {\r\n	$(function() {\r\n		$(''.tab-container .tab-title a'').on(''click'', function() {\r\n			$(''.tab-container .tab-title a'').removeClass(''active'');\r\n			$(this).addClass(''active'');\r\n			$(''.tab-container .tab-content > div'').removeClass(''active'');\r\n			$(''.tab-container .tab-content .'' + $(this).data(''tab'')).addClass(''active'');\r\n			return false;\r\n		});\r\n	});\r\n})(jQuery);\r\n</script>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-2 newsletter">\r\n<h3>Newsletter</h3>\r\n<p class="sub-title">Subscribe to the E-newsletter and receive the latest and limited edition products news, exclusive offers and events information.</p>\r\n<div class="form-holder"><form action="{{store url=''newsletter/subscriber/new''}}" method="POST"><input placeholder="Please enter your email ..." type="email" name="email" /> <button type="submit"><span><span class="submit">Subscribe</span></span></button></form></div>\r\n<div class="social-buttons">\r\n<a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Renguangdo-%E4%BB%81%E5%85%89%E5%A0%82/170956312945173" target="_blank"><img src="{{media url="wysiwyg/icon-facebook.png"}}" alt="Facebook" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<style>\r\n	.tab-container .tab-content > div { display: none; padding: 20px 0; line-height: 20px; }\r\n	.tab-container .tab-content .active { display: block; }\r\n	.tab-container .tab-title { border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; }\r\n	.tab-container .tab-title ul li { display: inline-block; float: left; }\r\n	.tab-container .tab-title ul li a { background: #fff; color: #7b5e56; padding: 7px 30px; font-size: 20px; display: inline-block; border-width: 1px 1px 0; border-style: solid; border-color: #ddd; transition: all .3s ease-in-out; }\r\n	.tab-container .tab-title ul li:first-child a { border-right: none; }\r\n	.tab-container .tab-title ul li a:hover, .tab-container .tab-title ul li a.active { background: #7b5e56; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; }\r\n    .newsletter .sub-title { font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; margin: 0; padding: 0; color: #989898; line-height: 1.6em; }\r\n    .submit { text-transform: none; }\r\n</style>', 'Shop About Block', 'shop_about_block', 'test', 65, 2, 28, 25),
