(1151, '<div class="shop-about clearfix">\r\n<div class="col-1">\r\n<div class="tab-container">\r\n	<div class="tab-title">\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li><a class="active" href="#" data-tab="tab-beauty">平衡美學</a></li>\r\n			<li><a href="#" data-tab="tab-usda">有機認證</a></li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		<div class="clear"></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="tab-content">\r\n		<div class="active text tab-beauty">\r\n			<div class="logo"><img src="{{media url="wysiwyg/small-banner.png"}}" alt="" /></div>\r\n			<p>從水、油的恰度調和開始，體現仁光堂為你肌膚綻放的平衡美學。</p>\r\n			<p>仁光堂傳承茶花經年的養生智慧，以現代科技提煉茶花籽油，設計迎合不同肌質需要的茶花籽油產品，將茶花籽油的效能發揮極致，體現不過多、不過少的中庸美顏之道，從水、油的恰度調和開始，為你淨化肌膚，活化肌理，這就是專屬仁光堂的平衡美學。</p>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<div class="clear"></div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="text tab-usda">\r\n			<div class="logo"><img src="{{media url="wysiwyg/small-banner-2.png"}}" alt="" /></div>\r\n			<p>USDA有機認證 是美國農業部授權核可的官方有機認證標章，證明該產品原料生產過程皆符合嚴格規定，並禁止使用農藥、化肥、生長激素、化學殺蟲劑、化學除草劑、合成代用品、基因改造物並杜絕輻射等危險因素。除此之外，產品需含至少95%以上有機成分，才可於產品上標示USDA圓形有機標章，是完整且可信賴的國際有機標章。</p>\r\n			<p>仁光堂以純正山茶花籽油 ( USDA 認証 ) 作為創作平台的製作出一系列高質素護膚護髮產品，以照顧各種不同多種肌膚及頭髮的需要。</p>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<div class="clear"></div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<script type="text/javascript">\r\n(function($) {\r\n	$(function() {\r\n		$(''.tab-container .tab-title a'').on(''click'', function() {\r\n			$(''.tab-container .tab-title a'').removeClass(''active'');\r\n			$(this).addClass(''active'');\r\n			$(''.tab-container .tab-content > div'').removeClass(''active'');\r\n			$(''.tab-container .tab-content .'' + $(this).data(''tab'')).addClass(''active'');\r\n			return false;\r\n		});\r\n	});\r\n})(jQuery);\r\n</script>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-2 newsletter">\r\n<h3>訂閱電子報</h3>\r\n<p class="sub-title">訂閱電子報可獲得RenGuangDo最新及限量版產品情報，獨家優惠及活動資訊。</p>\r\n<div class="form-holder"><form action="{{store url=''newsletter/subscriber/new''}}" method="POST"><input placeholder="請輸入你的電子郵件" type="email" name="email" /> <button type="submit"><span><span>登記</span></span></button></form></div>\r\n<div class="social-buttons">\r\n<a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Renguangdo-%E4%BB%81%E5%85%89%E5%A0%82/170956312945173" target="_blank"><img src="{{media url="wysiwyg/icon-facebook.png"}}" alt="Facebook" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<style>\r\n	.tab-container .tab-content > div { display: none; padding: 20px 0; line-height: 20px; }\r\n	.tab-container .tab-content .active { display: block; }\r\n	.tab-container .tab-title { border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; }\r\n	.tab-container .tab-title ul li { display: inline-block; float: left; }\r\n	.tab-container .tab-title ul li a { background: #fff; color: #7b5e56; padding: 7px 30px; font-size: 20px; display: inline-block; border-width: 1px 1px 0; border-style: solid; border-color: #ddd; transition: all .3s ease-in-out; }\r\n	.tab-container .tab-title ul li:first-child a { border-right: none; }\r\n	.tab-container .tab-title ul li a:hover, .tab-container .tab-title ul li a.active { background: #7b5e56; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; }\r\n        .newsletter .sub-title { font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; margin: 0; padding: 0; color: #989898; line-height: 1.6em; }\r\n</style>', 'Shop About Block', 'shop_about_block', '仁光堂線上商店', 65, 2, 5, 80),
